WEBVTT

01:37.000 --> 01:40.979
[The Best Thing]

01:41.410 --> 01:48.820
[Episode 12: Semen Cassiae: Sweet, Bitter, Salty in Taste, Slightly Cold in Nature, Belongs to the Liver and Large Intestine Meridians, Clears Heat and Improves Vision]

02:24.520 --> 02:25.680
What am I doing?

02:26.020 --> 02:28.220
I'm just here to ask him to revise my application materials.

02:28.250 --> 02:29.720
What am I thinking about?

02:34.760 --> 02:36.300
Here, have some soup.

02:36.320 --> 02:37.270
This is chicken soup, you know.

02:37.300 --> 02:38.140
Okay.

02:38.470 --> 02:39.820
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.310
That's enough.

02:43.150 --> 02:44.450
By the way, Dad.

02:44.960 --> 02:45.450
Mom.

02:46.560 --> 02:47.520
I've already sent my application materials

02:47.520 --> 02:49.150
to the study abroad agency.

02:49.150 --> 02:50.470
They will forward them to the school.

02:51.240 --> 02:52.030
That's good.

02:52.030 --> 02:53.680
At least one thing is done.

02:54.320 --> 02:55.520
What did the agency say?

02:55.550 --> 02:57.320
Do they think you can get the offer?

02:58.310 --> 02:59.360
I've added all the practical cases

02:59.360 --> 03:01.090
from this period.

03:01.280 --> 03:03.430
The agency said the content is quite rich.

03:03.610 --> 03:05.500
I just hope it gets approved now.

03:05.800 --> 03:07.240
Sounds like there's hope.

03:09.870 --> 03:10.630
Keep it up.

03:10.630 --> 03:11.040
Okay.

03:20.150 --> 03:21.050
Li Jie has left.

03:33.930 --> 03:35.860
Sir, two donuts, please.

03:36.350 --> 03:37.510
Alright. Coming right up.

03:48.000 --> 03:48.600
Here.

03:49.250 --> 03:49.970
Thank you.

03:56.540 --> 03:57.329
Oh right,

03:58.030 --> 03:59.400
what did the agency contact you about today?

03:59.630 --> 04:00.800
Did they need any materials?

04:02.750 --> 04:04.030
There's no problem with the materials,

04:04.030 --> 04:05.400
just some minor edits needed.

04:07.330 --> 04:08.600
So, if you get the offer,

04:08.630 --> 04:09.880
when can you go abroad?

04:13.870 --> 04:14.460
Feb-

04:14.970 --> 04:15.760
February.

04:16.970 --> 04:17.850
February?

04:42.150 --> 04:48.159
[The time difference between China and Switzerland]

05:02.630 --> 05:08.680
♫You're like a gentle wind♫

05:09.440 --> 05:14.510
♫After early summer afternoon, it blows past my heart♫

05:14.890 --> 05:16.890
I have to go abroad in February.

05:16.380 --> 05:22.320
♫When your fingers touch my hands♫

05:17.790 --> 05:19.520
With a seven-hour time difference

05:20.590 --> 05:21.960
and such a long distance,

05:23.220 --> 05:27.920
♫So you're also here for me♫

05:23.440 --> 05:24.710
I guess

05:25.270 --> 05:28.160
I probably won't be able to see Dr. He for a long time.

05:29.930 --> 05:35.570
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

05:32.310 --> 05:33.070
Shen Xifan,

05:33.530 --> 05:34.930
being your boyfriend is too exhausting.

05:36.240 --> 05:37.000
You going abroad to study

05:37.000 --> 05:38.560
will cause so much trouble for the people around you.

05:37.010 --> 05:39.350
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

05:39.310 --> 05:41.070
Why am I only realizing now that you're so selfish?

05:40.350 --> 05:43.600
♫Cherish the youth♫

05:42.190 --> 05:42.780
Forget it.

05:43.240 --> 05:44.240
Think about it yourself.

05:45.380 --> 05:51.400
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

05:47.970 --> 05:50.680
Maybe it's time for me to wake up.

05:52.290 --> 05:57.650
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

05:59.150 --> 06:05.000
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

06:05.970 --> 06:11.400
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

06:40.210 --> 06:41.770
The overall content is fine.

06:43.240 --> 06:45.920
Next, you'll need to add some more cases.

06:47.260 --> 06:48.540
This topic is excellent.

06:48.560 --> 06:49.560
It's very meaningful.

06:51.040 --> 06:51.950
Breast cancer

06:52.550 --> 06:55.310
is one of the most common tumors among women.

06:56.890 --> 06:57.760
However,

06:57.830 --> 06:59.790
though it has the highest incidence rate,

07:01.390 --> 07:02.190
breast cancer

07:02.560 --> 07:05.710
is preventable, treatable, and curable.

07:06.350 --> 07:07.610
At present, in our country,

07:08.790 --> 07:11.590
we have already established a relatively complete and mature system

07:11.590 --> 07:13.960
for early screening and treatment

07:14.200 --> 07:15.710
of breast cancer,

07:15.710 --> 07:17.350
which benefits many women.

07:17.830 --> 07:19.470
This is very significant.

07:20.200 --> 07:22.390
During the treatment of breast cancer,

07:22.760 --> 07:24.470
how to use TCM methods

07:24.470 --> 07:27.230
to alleviate patients' suffering

07:27.500 --> 07:30.020
and help female patients

07:30.040 --> 07:32.159
develop a healthy, positive mindset

07:32.630 --> 07:33.860
to face both their illness

07:33.909 --> 07:35.120
and future

07:35.350 --> 07:37.909
is the direction we will explore next.

07:40.640 --> 07:41.390
Yes.

07:41.710 --> 07:42.710
Besides,

07:42.710 --> 07:43.760
this is also

07:43.760 --> 07:45.520
our original intention for choosing this topic this time.

07:49.230 --> 07:51.320
Let's end our discussion here for today.

07:51.320 --> 07:52.270
Everyone, take a break.

07:52.790 --> 07:53.560
Thank you, Professor.

08:00.230 --> 08:02.430
Suye, are you in a hurry to go back today as well?

08:05.550 --> 08:07.420
Yesterday, I accidentally interrupted

08:07.450 --> 08:09.450
his date with Manager Shen.

08:10.690 --> 08:12.910
If you have another date today,

08:12.910 --> 08:14.230
don't waste any time.

08:14.400 --> 08:15.520
Just go.

08:15.830 --> 08:16.740
Shen...

08:16.760 --> 08:18.000
Shen Xifan?

08:19.560 --> 08:20.680
It's not a date.

08:21.080 --> 08:23.470
I'm just meeting her to discuss something.

08:24.810 --> 08:26.010
At home.

08:26.350 --> 08:26.960
At home?

08:26.960 --> 08:27.680
At home?

08:28.150 --> 08:28.910
At home?

08:35.590 --> 08:36.990
It's nothing. It's just that...

08:36.990 --> 08:38.850
we live in the same neighborhood,

08:39.159 --> 08:41.159
so it's more convenient to talk at home.

08:41.159 --> 08:41.679
Yes.

08:42.940 --> 08:43.940
It's more convenient at home.

08:44.990 --> 08:45.870
It's more convenient at home.

08:46.150 --> 08:48.180
There's no cafe in the neighborhood.

08:49.730 --> 08:50.850
No cafe, huh?

08:59.350 --> 09:00.280
I'm still pursuing her.

09:00.870 --> 09:01.680
Still what?

09:02.680 --> 09:03.850
Still pursuing her.

09:04.600 --> 09:05.400
You're still...

09:06.080 --> 09:07.230
Have you won her over?

09:07.640 --> 09:09.280
Since I'm still pursuing her, how could I have won her over?

09:09.790 --> 09:11.550
You pursued her all the way to her house?

09:28.630 --> 09:29.230
Dr. He,

09:29.230 --> 09:29.960
congratulations.

09:29.960 --> 09:30.630
Go for it.

09:34.960 --> 09:36.430
Go for it, Dr. He.

09:38.910 --> 09:40.270
You can do it, Dr. He.

09:53.630 --> 09:55.560
I was wondering why you didn't go to the blind date event

09:55.560 --> 09:56.470
last time.

09:56.590 --> 09:58.710
Turns out, you already have someone in mind.

10:00.470 --> 10:01.750
You guys really like gossip.

10:01.750 --> 10:02.410
It's alright.

10:02.750 --> 10:04.080
I guess everyone in the hospital knows by now?

10:04.080 --> 10:04.990
Basically, yeah.

10:06.080 --> 10:06.960
Is she pretty?

10:07.110 --> 10:08.350
Let's have dinner sometime,

10:08.350 --> 10:09.630
and you should ask her out so we can check her out.

10:11.080 --> 10:12.610
Don't rush.

10:12.760 --> 10:13.930
I haven't won her over yet.

10:14.550 --> 10:17.700
Who is she? Which girl is so hard to pursue?

10:17.920 --> 10:18.470
Got a photo?

10:18.470 --> 10:19.470
I'll help you analyze it

10:19.470 --> 10:20.230
and give you some advice.

10:21.430 --> 10:22.080
You?

10:22.180 --> 10:23.160
Give me some advice?

10:24.470 --> 10:25.320
Save it.

10:26.230 --> 10:27.400
Are you looking down on me?

10:27.400 --> 10:28.510
I'm quite experienced.

10:29.400 --> 10:30.040
Really.

10:31.110 --> 10:32.160
Let me take a look!

10:51.120 --> 10:52.080
Let me check out the news.

10:59.440 --> 11:01.560
This one's interesting.

11:03.280 --> 11:06.440
Most of today's post-1995 generation are single

11:06.440 --> 11:09.040
because their social circles are too small.

11:09.870 --> 11:11.800
They prefer staying at home,

11:11.800 --> 11:12.920
don't socialize much,

11:13.200 --> 11:14.400
are busy with work,

11:14.750 --> 11:17.400
and have really high standards for a partner.

11:17.990 --> 11:19.680
Ms. Liu, look at this news.

11:19.680 --> 11:21.630
It's a vicious cycle, you know?

11:21.630 --> 11:22.230
Really?

11:22.230 --> 11:22.830
Think about it.

11:23.280 --> 11:24.280
You don't socialize,

11:24.470 --> 11:26.110
so your social circle is inevitably small,

11:26.110 --> 11:27.590
but your standards for a partner

11:27.590 --> 11:28.590
are still super high.

11:29.400 --> 11:30.800
This news really

11:31.320 --> 11:32.230
hits the...

11:32.230 --> 11:34.200
Why are you yelling?

11:34.470 --> 11:35.870
You're putting pressure on our Ms. Shen.

11:36.230 --> 11:37.160
I'm not.

11:37.440 --> 11:38.400
I'm sorry, Ms. Shen.

11:38.560 --> 11:39.750
Can you learn from me?

11:40.560 --> 11:41.990
Since the last time she went on a blind date

11:41.990 --> 11:43.590
with that little TCM guy and it didn't work out,

11:43.590 --> 11:44.320
did I mention it?

11:44.320 --> 11:44.800
No.

11:44.800 --> 11:45.710
Did I mention it?

11:45.710 --> 11:46.580
No, you didn't.

11:46.710 --> 11:49.200
Whether he's a golden-collar worker in a foreign enterprise

11:49.560 --> 11:49.990
or a tall, handsome guy

11:49.990 --> 11:51.110
working in the government,

11:51.110 --> 11:51.800
it's all useless.

11:52.330 --> 11:53.260
You can't force it.

11:53.280 --> 11:53.960
True.

11:54.160 --> 11:55.500
That's right.

11:56.400 --> 11:57.200
Wait.

11:57.370 --> 11:58.890
Before concluding that it's forced,

12:00.280 --> 12:01.870
she should look at the photo first.

12:01.870 --> 12:04.750
Right? What if he gives a good impression?

12:05.510 --> 12:06.350
Right?

12:06.630 --> 12:07.560
Take a look at his photo.

12:08.750 --> 12:09.680
Ms. Liu.

12:10.680 --> 12:11.510
It...

12:12.860 --> 12:14.380
Why are you talking to me?

12:14.440 --> 12:15.440
Talk to your dad.

12:15.440 --> 12:17.040
I'm not the one who read the news.

12:19.960 --> 12:20.960
Mr. Shen,

12:21.340 --> 12:22.220
It doesn't...

12:22.800 --> 12:24.360
seem appropriate, does it?

12:25.780 --> 12:26.540
What's wrong?

12:27.150 --> 12:29.860
What if his goal is marriage?

12:30.180 --> 12:32.580
But what about me? I'm going abroad to study.

12:32.890 --> 12:34.750
That will be a huge gap

12:34.750 --> 12:36.120
between the two of us.

12:36.140 --> 12:37.340
It's not appropriate.

12:38.750 --> 12:39.920
That makes sense.

12:41.230 --> 12:41.960
That...

12:41.960 --> 12:42.400
Wait.

12:42.400 --> 12:43.160
Make sense?

12:43.350 --> 12:43.710
Really?

12:43.710 --> 12:44.320
Does it make sense?

12:44.320 --> 12:44.560
No.

12:44.560 --> 12:45.200
Yes, it does make sense.

12:45.200 --> 12:45.960
It makes a bit of sense.

12:45.960 --> 12:46.560
You see,

12:46.770 --> 12:49.020
what Ms. Shen is thinking about is life planning.

12:49.040 --> 12:50.240
So,

12:50.270 --> 12:51.580
we should look at the photo first.

12:52.300 --> 12:53.540
Let's look at the photo.

12:53.790 --> 12:55.030
The photo is...

12:55.480 --> 12:56.240
here.

12:58.510 --> 12:59.390
What are you doing?

13:01.810 --> 13:02.920
I forgot to open it earlier,

13:02.920 --> 13:03.990
and the photo has expired.

13:04.310 --> 13:04.630
Look.

13:04.630 --> 13:05.630
B-But...

13:07.620 --> 13:08.380
But...

13:08.800 --> 13:10.200
you can still see

13:10.200 --> 13:12.280
his general shape.

13:13.290 --> 13:13.860
Ms. Shen.

13:15.400 --> 13:15.960
Ms. Shen.

13:17.990 --> 13:20.400
Let me take a look at his general shape.

13:21.500 --> 13:23.690
Square-shaped, not bad.

13:25.750 --> 13:26.920
Ms. Shen,

13:26.920 --> 13:28.440
I'll send you his name

13:28.440 --> 13:29.710
and phone number now.

13:29.710 --> 13:30.080
Also,

13:30.080 --> 13:31.200
I've made an appointment for you.

13:31.200 --> 13:32.550
I'll send you the name of the restaurant.

13:32.570 --> 13:33.970
Remember to be there on Friday night.

13:35.560 --> 13:36.870
You made an appointment so soon?

13:37.630 --> 13:38.440
Is it too soon?

13:38.460 --> 13:38.940
Is it too soon?

13:39.340 --> 13:40.620
Is Friday too soon?

13:40.640 --> 13:42.420
We naturally made

13:42.450 --> 13:43.340
the appointment.

13:43.370 --> 13:45.370
It's not even today.

13:45.390 --> 13:46.430
I don't think it's too soon.

13:46.460 --> 13:47.180
Yeah.

13:47.870 --> 13:48.590
This is great.

13:48.590 --> 13:49.560
Let's read more news

13:49.800 --> 13:51.260
while eating in the future.

13:51.920 --> 13:53.830
I'll have to deal with them again.

14:05.680 --> 14:06.680
Ms. Liu,

14:06.750 --> 14:08.630
why hasn't the guy I'm on the blind date with

14:08.630 --> 14:10.040
come yet?

14:10.190 --> 14:11.740
Ask him for me.

14:17.280 --> 14:18.490
Hello, Miss.

14:18.520 --> 14:19.760
Would you like to order now?

14:21.080 --> 14:22.040
Sorry.

14:22.040 --> 14:23.440
My friend is not here yet.

14:23.440 --> 14:24.870
Can you wait a little longer?

14:34.920 --> 14:35.710
He's late?

14:36.230 --> 14:37.110
Let me ask him.

14:45.870 --> 14:46.660
Miss,

14:46.710 --> 14:47.870
have some candies first.

14:47.870 --> 14:49.200
Take your time.

14:50.080 --> 14:50.630
Thank you.

15:05.960 --> 15:06.750
Xiangya,

15:06.750 --> 15:08.800
this is ridiculous, absolutely ridiculous.

15:08.880 --> 15:10.430
I got stood up on my blind date.

15:11.070 --> 15:14.830
How about coming out and hanging out with me later?

15:21.920 --> 15:22.710
Ms. Shen,

15:22.990 --> 15:24.230
I can't reach him.

15:24.480 --> 15:25.510
Why don't you leave first?

15:25.510 --> 15:26.470
Find a nice restaurant

15:26.500 --> 15:27.620
and eat something delicious.

15:27.640 --> 15:29.830
I already gave that matchmaker a good scolding.

15:30.130 --> 15:31.440
He's so rude.

15:45.350 --> 15:46.200
Manager Shen.

15:48.320 --> 15:49.170
Li Jie.

15:49.200 --> 15:50.560
What a coincidence.

15:50.560 --> 15:51.560
Why are you here?

15:52.800 --> 15:54.320
I'm here to meet a friend.

15:54.680 --> 15:55.630
Why are you here?

15:56.510 --> 15:57.470
We're having a class reunion.

15:59.630 --> 16:01.400
Well, have fun at the reunion.

16:01.400 --> 16:02.630
I'm going out to find a place to eat.

16:02.630 --> 16:03.650
It's a little expensive here.

16:03.670 --> 16:04.320
Wait a minute.

16:04.680 --> 16:05.680
Suye asked

16:05.920 --> 16:06.830
if you want to join us.

16:16.540 --> 16:18.030
I saw Manager Shen.

16:21.160 --> 16:21.870
Excuse me.

16:23.030 --> 16:23.630
Hello.

16:24.280 --> 16:25.200
I'm sorry.

16:25.200 --> 16:26.680
My friend probably won't come.

16:26.860 --> 16:28.220
May I just pay the bill?

16:28.470 --> 16:28.990
Here?

16:28.990 --> 16:30.040
How would you like to pay?

16:30.040 --> 16:30.710
She got stood up.

16:30.710 --> 16:31.710
WeChat pay, please.

16:32.750 --> 16:33.200
Okay.

16:33.470 --> 16:34.110
Scan this.

16:36.920 --> 16:37.630
Isn't it inappropriate?

16:37.630 --> 16:39.530
It's your reunion. I shouldn't be there.

16:39.800 --> 16:41.350
There's nothing inappropriate.

16:41.350 --> 16:42.990
We're colleagues and classmates.

16:43.590 --> 16:45.080
Everyone is easy to get along with.

16:46.680 --> 16:47.830
Come on.

16:49.560 --> 16:50.590
Don't hesitate.

16:50.590 --> 16:51.640
Let's hang out together.

16:53.350 --> 16:54.230
I'll just...

16:54.230 --> 16:55.080
Don't reject me.

17:00.560 --> 17:01.090
Okay.

17:01.320 --> 17:02.590
Let's go. That private room.

17:02.770 --> 17:03.220
Okay.

17:03.240 --> 17:04.119
Just walk straight ahead.

17:06.680 --> 17:08.030
We ordered a lot of dishes.

17:08.920 --> 17:10.240
It's Suye's treat today.

17:12.710 --> 17:14.599
When you introduce Manager Shen, say she's your friend,

17:14.819 --> 17:15.859
in case people make a fuss.

17:17.390 --> 17:18.150
Li Jie,

17:18.510 --> 17:19.160
what's wrong?

17:19.960 --> 17:20.839
Nothing. Let's go.

17:22.900 --> 17:23.730
This room.

17:23.750 --> 17:24.230
This one?

17:29.390 --> 17:30.390
Excuse me,

17:30.440 --> 17:31.070
waitress.

17:31.420 --> 17:33.530
Please bring me two more bottles of Tuopai Special.

17:33.550 --> 17:35.230
We must drink to our heart's content today.

17:35.230 --> 17:36.400
We must drink heartily today.

17:36.400 --> 17:37.360
You're drunk.

17:37.360 --> 17:39.400
It's for fun. We're here today to have fun, aren't we?

17:39.400 --> 17:39.960
Everyone,

17:40.200 --> 17:41.750
I brought a friend here.

17:58.950 --> 18:00.280
Let me introduce her.

18:00.700 --> 18:02.500
This is Shen Xifan.

18:02.970 --> 18:04.690
She's a friend of mine.

18:05.360 --> 18:07.270
She's here for dinner, but there are no tables available.

18:07.270 --> 18:08.960
So I brought her here to join us for a meal.

18:09.070 --> 18:10.600
Hope you don't mind.

18:11.640 --> 18:12.400
Sorry to bother.

18:13.680 --> 18:15.400
Welcome! Welcome!

18:15.400 --> 18:16.710
We warmly welcome you!

18:16.710 --> 18:18.790
Welcome!

18:18.790 --> 18:20.120
We warmly welcome you!

18:20.640 --> 18:21.160
Good!

18:21.830 --> 18:22.700
Welcome, welcome!

18:23.680 --> 18:25.310
These are all my seniors and juniors

18:25.310 --> 18:26.920
from the oncology department.

18:26.920 --> 18:27.840
They are all very nice people,

18:27.840 --> 18:28.880
very easy to get along with.

18:28.880 --> 18:29.400
That's right.

18:29.680 --> 18:30.550
Well...

18:31.360 --> 18:32.640
let me make a formal introduction.

18:32.640 --> 18:33.400
I am

18:33.400 --> 18:34.360
his senior.

18:35.120 --> 18:36.510
People always say doctors are benevolent.

18:36.510 --> 18:37.810
We're really super kind.

18:37.830 --> 18:38.620
Come, sit here.

18:42.400 --> 18:43.070
Fang.

18:44.310 --> 18:44.790
Fang?

18:46.310 --> 18:48.220
Don't you think it's a bit crowded?

18:48.600 --> 18:50.120
Move over a little.

18:50.120 --> 18:50.750
Sit here.

18:50.750 --> 18:51.360
Thank you.

18:51.360 --> 18:52.400
Excuse me.

18:52.400 --> 18:53.270
Please bring one more set of utensils.

18:53.270 --> 18:54.120
And one more chair.

18:54.440 --> 18:55.950
I'll go hurry her up.

19:00.360 --> 19:00.840
Fang,

19:01.360 --> 19:02.310
take care of her.

19:05.120 --> 19:05.680
I'm sorry for the trouble.

19:05.990 --> 19:06.960
Please wait a moment.

19:10.840 --> 19:11.640
It's been a long time since we last gathered.

19:11.640 --> 19:13.030
Let's all have a drink together.

19:13.030 --> 19:14.360
Come on, come on.

19:14.360 --> 19:14.920
Cheers.

19:14.920 --> 19:15.880
Bottoms up.

19:16.310 --> 19:17.030
Bottoms up.

19:17.640 --> 19:18.750
Finally, everyone's here.

19:18.750 --> 19:19.510
It's the first time.

19:19.510 --> 19:20.120
Yes, yes.

19:20.880 --> 19:22.120
Drink a little more.

19:22.120 --> 19:23.470
Later, let's go to

19:23.470 --> 19:24.360
the after-party.

19:24.360 --> 19:25.710
Are you treating us to the after-party?

19:25.710 --> 19:26.790
Can you treat us to the after-party?

19:26.790 --> 19:27.840
Of course.

19:29.230 --> 19:29.710
Hey,

19:30.400 --> 19:31.030
Miss Shen.

19:31.620 --> 19:34.750
I heard you're working at Gunan Huating Hotel.

19:34.920 --> 19:35.360
Yes.

19:36.200 --> 19:39.230
The fact that you work there shows you're capable.

19:39.230 --> 19:39.880
No, no.

19:39.880 --> 19:40.860
I can't compare to you guys.

19:40.890 --> 19:42.720
Modest. You're being modest again.

19:43.030 --> 19:45.310
Your modesty makes me want to ask,

19:46.510 --> 19:47.990
how did you and Li know each other?

19:54.510 --> 19:55.750
We worked together

19:55.750 --> 19:58.120
on a traditional Chinese medicine project before.

19:58.120 --> 20:00.160
We hired him as a consultant.

20:01.680 --> 20:02.990
Oh, I know that.

20:03.070 --> 20:04.060
I know that. I know that.

20:04.080 --> 20:07.110
I remember that project was led by He, right?

20:08.120 --> 20:08.470
Yes.

20:08.680 --> 20:10.400
Dr. He was also in the team at the time.

20:10.400 --> 20:11.470
We've all met before.

20:11.470 --> 20:12.230
And Fang was there too.

20:14.750 --> 20:15.680
Speaking of He...

20:15.680 --> 20:16.470
This is from Senior He.

20:16.470 --> 20:17.810
Thank you.

20:21.210 --> 20:22.580
Lotus.

20:25.030 --> 20:26.270
I want to eat Tangyuan too.

20:28.200 --> 20:28.510
Lo...

20:31.080 --> 20:31.920
I've been drinking.

20:31.920 --> 20:33.230
My stomach hurts. As you know,

20:33.230 --> 20:34.950
my stomach's always been bad.

20:34.970 --> 20:35.510
Alright, alright.

20:35.510 --> 20:36.600
Give it to me.

20:39.400 --> 20:40.270
How many?

20:41.980 --> 20:44.070
Before I decide,

20:44.090 --> 20:45.480
I have something to say.

20:46.200 --> 20:46.750
You can't

20:47.210 --> 20:49.380
just take care of our new friend

20:49.400 --> 20:51.230
and forget about me, your old friend.

20:51.470 --> 20:53.560
That'll really break my heart.

20:54.470 --> 20:55.360
How many?

20:55.510 --> 20:56.140
Six.

20:58.660 --> 21:00.980
You eat this much and still can't get a girlfriend.

21:01.590 --> 21:03.590
I'm eating this much just to find a girlfriend.

21:03.710 --> 21:04.510
As the old saying goes,

21:04.510 --> 21:06.440
a big body doesn't lack strength, right?

21:06.440 --> 21:07.270
Okay.

21:09.060 --> 21:10.140
I found that

21:10.570 --> 21:13.330
you guys are only eating but not drinking.

21:13.790 --> 21:15.030
How about this?

21:15.510 --> 21:17.040
Let's play a game to spice things up,

21:17.230 --> 21:17.960
alright?

21:18.170 --> 21:20.540
Let's play Continue the Prescription.

21:20.560 --> 21:21.990
-Okay.
-Okay.

21:22.030 --> 21:22.400
Okay.

21:22.400 --> 21:23.600
We're having a great time here.

21:23.600 --> 21:25.120
And you want to review professional knowledge?

21:25.120 --> 21:25.550
Exactly.

21:25.550 --> 21:26.750
Are you trying to outwork us all?

21:27.370 --> 21:30.160
This is called "with good wine to lift the mood,

21:30.190 --> 21:31.640
we must drink in moderation."

21:31.680 --> 21:33.880
We can't just focus on having fun.

21:34.120 --> 21:35.960
We should also take the knowledge from our genes

21:35.960 --> 21:37.990
and refresh it, air it out,

21:37.990 --> 21:39.030
and sort it through.

21:39.030 --> 21:40.880
Continue the Prescription is too difficult.

21:40.880 --> 21:41.920
What about Miss Shen?

21:42.450 --> 21:43.360
How about this?

21:43.600 --> 21:44.370
Let's change the rule.

21:44.880 --> 21:45.840
Continue...

21:46.120 --> 21:46.750
the Medication?

21:47.230 --> 21:48.030
She should be able to do it.

21:50.520 --> 21:51.170
I'll give it a try.

21:51.400 --> 21:51.880
Good.

21:54.560 --> 21:55.120
How about this?

21:55.360 --> 21:57.470
If the rest of us can't continue,

21:57.750 --> 21:59.020
we'll take a shot.

21:59.120 --> 22:00.550
If Miss Shen can't, she'll just have a little, alright?

22:00.750 --> 22:03.270
Sounds good. That's how it should be.

22:03.270 --> 22:04.570
It must be like this.

22:04.590 --> 22:06.830
-Okay, I'll start.
-Come on.

22:09.030 --> 22:09.790
Gui Zhi.

22:10.530 --> 22:11.370
Gui Pi.

22:11.990 --> 22:13.030
Pomegranate peel.

22:13.790 --> 22:15.230
Pomegranate peel?

22:15.230 --> 22:16.070
That doesn't count!

22:16.070 --> 22:16.710
That doesn't count!

22:17.330 --> 22:18.570
Pomegranate peel?

22:19.030 --> 22:20.400
Pomegranate peel doesn't count.

22:20.400 --> 22:21.790
Alright, alright.

22:21.790 --> 22:23.640
I didn't bring the Chinese Pharmacopoeia today.

22:23.640 --> 22:24.840
Otherwise, I'd let you know

22:24.840 --> 22:25.880
what pomegranate peel is.

22:25.880 --> 22:26.310
I'll drink.

22:27.470 --> 22:28.230
What is he talking about?

22:28.230 --> 22:30.270
Let's stop talking.

22:30.270 --> 22:31.790
One, two, three, four.

22:35.550 --> 22:36.470
Baishao.

22:38.040 --> 22:38.880
Shaoyao!

22:42.090 --> 22:43.200
Let's start with another one.

22:43.200 --> 22:43.640
Hurry up.

22:46.360 --> 22:47.120
Su He Xiang!

22:49.050 --> 22:50.890
Su...

22:50.920 --> 22:51.510
Su Ye!

22:53.680 --> 22:54.550
Su Ye?

22:54.550 --> 22:56.790
What is Su Ye?

22:56.990 --> 22:58.440
What is Su Ye?

22:58.440 --> 22:59.510
If Su Ye counts,

22:59.510 --> 23:00.680
then my pomegranate peel counts too,

23:00.680 --> 23:02.120
right?

23:02.120 --> 23:02.990
Pomegranate...

23:02.990 --> 23:03.510
Su Ye

23:03.510 --> 23:03.880
counts.

23:03.880 --> 23:04.920
It doesn't.

23:05.270 --> 23:06.360
Am I a clown or what?

23:08.030 --> 23:10.160
There's no problem.

23:10.310 --> 23:11.440
Am I overthinking it?

24:22.880 --> 24:23.790
Why did you come out?

24:26.360 --> 24:27.460
There are too many people in the room.

24:28.130 --> 24:29.640
I was afraid you might feel uncomfortable and want to leave,

24:30.440 --> 24:31.440
so...

24:35.030 --> 24:35.990
Everyone is nice.

24:36.750 --> 24:37.400
Don't worry.

24:42.440 --> 24:43.510
Let's go back in.

24:44.640 --> 24:45.150
Okay.

24:58.910 --> 24:59.790
Tonight...

25:01.630 --> 25:02.870
who stood you up?

25:15.280 --> 25:16.480
You usually go straight home

25:17.260 --> 25:18.630
after work.

25:22.070 --> 25:24.260
Who were you going to meet tonight?

25:40.550 --> 25:41.360
A friend.

25:42.420 --> 25:43.070
A blind date?

25:49.450 --> 25:50.650
Looks like I guessed right.

25:59.070 --> 25:59.960
But that's fine.

26:01.030 --> 26:03.140
You got stood up

26:04.990 --> 26:05.840
and didn't get to see him.

26:22.750 --> 26:23.600
Let's...

26:25.270 --> 26:26.360
go home together tonight.

26:44.640 --> 26:45.740
I didn't drink,

26:45.760 --> 26:46.670
so I can drive.

27:06.650 --> 27:07.310
Let's go.

27:29.740 --> 27:30.980
Are you happy, Suye?

27:31.470 --> 27:33.200
I'm happy!

27:38.550 --> 27:40.350
Sing a song.

27:41.030 --> 27:41.750
You can do it.

27:43.610 --> 27:45.720
Come on, sing a song.

27:48.020 --> 27:49.540
Caifang, can you sing?

27:50.200 --> 27:51.960
Sing a song!

27:51.960 --> 27:52.640
Come on!

27:52.640 --> 27:53.510
You can do it!

27:55.230 --> 27:57.400
I caught you two.

28:00.180 --> 28:01.020
You're avoiding drinking

28:01.590 --> 28:03.070
and hiding in the corner.

28:03.810 --> 28:04.720
That's unacceptable.

28:04.750 --> 28:06.530
You must be punished.

28:06.640 --> 28:09.200
Either drink three shots of white wine

28:09.470 --> 28:11.880
or play truth or dare.

28:13.710 --> 28:15.360
I can't drink.

28:15.360 --> 28:16.600
That's great.

28:17.160 --> 28:17.990
Lotus,

28:17.990 --> 28:19.040
drink for her.

28:19.060 --> 28:19.860
I can't.

28:20.280 --> 28:21.430
Six shots of white wine

28:21.510 --> 28:22.640
for six Tangyuans.

28:22.640 --> 28:24.390
I can't. I have to drive later.

28:24.420 --> 28:24.990
What?

28:24.990 --> 28:26.760
How about truth or dare?

28:26.880 --> 28:27.710
Yeah!

28:28.270 --> 28:32.030
Truth!

28:32.030 --> 28:34.470
I'll drink, I'll drink.

28:34.470 --> 28:35.270
Hold on.

28:36.640 --> 28:37.600
I...

28:38.280 --> 28:39.200
I chose truth.

28:41.440 --> 28:43.710
Wonderful!

28:45.120 --> 28:46.440
Here's the question.

28:47.400 --> 28:50.400
There's a rumor going around the hospital that you have a crush now.

28:50.990 --> 28:53.500
Is that true?

29:03.270 --> 29:03.960
Yes.

29:07.230 --> 29:08.470
What?

29:08.470 --> 29:09.510
You're pretty cool.

29:09.510 --> 29:10.560
You just said yes.

29:10.680 --> 29:12.360
Does that mean

29:12.360 --> 29:14.440
the only one left single now is me?

29:15.200 --> 29:16.120
Wait a second.

29:16.600 --> 29:17.510
Who is it?

29:17.880 --> 29:18.360
Who is it?

29:18.360 --> 29:19.070
Who's the girl?

29:19.070 --> 29:20.360
Do I know her?

29:20.710 --> 29:22.680
I need to hurry up and remind her

29:22.680 --> 29:24.790
to switch to a cassia seed pillow.

29:24.880 --> 29:26.360
I want her to clear the heat and improve her eyesight

29:26.360 --> 29:28.880
so she can see your true face.

29:28.880 --> 29:30.030
What true face?

29:30.050 --> 29:31.310
We agreed on one question at a time.

29:31.310 --> 29:32.510
You've asked one, so it's over now.

29:32.510 --> 29:33.680
It's not over. Come on.

29:33.680 --> 29:34.270
Just tell us.

29:34.270 --> 29:35.470
Who is it?

29:35.470 --> 29:37.470
Who is it?

29:37.470 --> 29:38.270
Just tell us.

29:38.920 --> 29:39.710
Well...

29:43.840 --> 29:44.920
It's...

29:46.580 --> 29:48.580
It's just a girl I met in April.

29:51.470 --> 29:52.920
A girl you met in April?

29:52.920 --> 29:53.360
Did you hear that?

29:53.360 --> 29:54.790
-April.
-Did you hear that?

29:54.790 --> 29:55.990
Did you hear that?

29:56.710 --> 29:58.880
What is it?

30:00.310 --> 30:01.600
What April?

30:01.600 --> 30:04.230
It's still a little cold in April. Remember to dress warmly.

30:15.190 --> 30:16.110
Sorry.

30:16.230 --> 30:17.240
Did I hit you?

30:19.840 --> 30:20.630
I'm fine.

30:21.890 --> 30:23.100
I'm sorry.

30:30.740 --> 30:33.590
I was in the hospital in April.

30:34.800 --> 30:36.340
How could I not know?

30:36.360 --> 30:39.200
How could I let you get her?

30:40.670 --> 30:42.600
I'm even more confused now.

30:45.910 --> 30:46.880
Be careful.

30:47.990 --> 30:48.580
Senior He,

30:48.910 --> 30:50.960
how about I take Manager Shen home for you?

30:50.960 --> 30:52.070
It's okay. I live in the same neighborhood as her.

30:52.070 --> 30:53.030
I'll just send her home.

30:53.790 --> 30:54.510
Look behind you.

30:54.510 --> 30:55.680
There are so many people who need you to take care of.

30:55.680 --> 30:57.440
I won't go home.

30:57.440 --> 30:57.960
Li Jie.

30:58.990 --> 30:59.600
Li Jie!

31:00.140 --> 31:02.070
I'll leave the rest of them to you and Fang!

31:02.200 --> 31:02.710
Okay!

31:03.180 --> 31:03.660
Be careful.

31:03.680 --> 31:04.290
Let me do it.

31:04.740 --> 31:05.460
We're leaving.

31:05.480 --> 31:06.200
I'll do it.

31:06.960 --> 31:07.770
Watch the steps.

31:31.790 --> 31:32.430
Be careful.

31:32.430 --> 31:33.120
You're drunk.

31:38.310 --> 31:40.200
Thank you for liking me.

31:41.220 --> 31:41.940
What?

31:53.420 --> 31:54.420
I said...

31:57.570 --> 31:59.640
thank you for liking me.

32:07.570 --> 32:08.610
You're drunk.

32:26.290 --> 32:27.180
I'm not.

32:35.720 --> 32:36.960
What did you just say?

32:38.180 --> 32:39.030
Say it again.

32:40.750 --> 32:41.990
I said...

32:44.200 --> 32:46.640
thank you for liking me.

33:34.200 --> 33:35.120
Mr. Shen?

33:35.120 --> 33:35.960
What's going on here?

33:35.960 --> 33:36.440
Ms. Shen,

33:36.440 --> 33:37.840
what happened to you?

33:37.840 --> 33:39.070
There's such a strong smell of alcohol.

33:39.590 --> 33:39.990
It's...

33:39.990 --> 33:41.310
What happened?

33:41.310 --> 33:42.120
I've been drinking.

33:42.120 --> 33:42.880
Come on, you...

33:42.880 --> 33:43.790
You've been drinking again?

33:43.790 --> 33:45.070
How could you drink again?

33:45.070 --> 33:46.030
Come on, come on.

33:46.030 --> 33:46.640
Help her get in.

33:46.640 --> 33:47.550
Be careful. Be careful.

33:48.230 --> 33:49.270
-Sir.
-Be careful.

33:50.510 --> 33:51.510
Who are you?

33:52.080 --> 33:53.470
I'm a friend of Xifan.

33:56.100 --> 33:57.170
Well, thank you then.

33:58.270 --> 33:59.030
You're welcome.

34:00.360 --> 34:01.680
Let me see the guest off first.

34:03.260 --> 34:04.630
Well, I'll leave now.

34:04.840 --> 34:05.270
Thank you.

34:05.270 --> 34:05.840
Okay.

34:06.840 --> 34:07.840
Well...

34:07.840 --> 34:08.590
You're leaving just like that?

34:08.590 --> 34:10.400
You must be exhausted

34:10.400 --> 34:11.590
from bringing our daughter back.

34:11.590 --> 34:12.800
How about you come in and sit for a while?

34:13.360 --> 34:14.469
Would you like to have some late-night snacks?

34:16.679 --> 34:17.280
Make some

34:17.280 --> 34:18.320
late-night snacks.

34:18.320 --> 34:19.150
Would you like some?

34:20.239 --> 34:21.710
I won't eat.

34:21.870 --> 34:23.469
I'm going back to rest first.

34:23.989 --> 34:24.360
Alright.

34:24.719 --> 34:25.070
Alright.

34:25.070 --> 34:25.670
Thank you.

34:25.670 --> 34:26.530
Thank you, Ma'am.

34:26.620 --> 34:28.350
How much did she drink?

34:28.469 --> 34:29.300
Exactly.

34:29.320 --> 34:30.159
Mr. and Mrs. Shen.

34:30.800 --> 34:32.880
How did you like the medicinal dishes you had before?

34:34.179 --> 34:35.820
Xifan asked me to make a few prescriptions,

34:35.870 --> 34:37.389
saying that you two would have them together.

34:39.760 --> 34:41.560
You're that Dr. He, right?

34:41.810 --> 34:42.850
Yes.

34:43.310 --> 34:44.719
I finally met you in person.

34:45.630 --> 34:47.360
Those medicinal dishes were so delicious.

34:47.360 --> 34:47.880
Really?

34:47.880 --> 34:49.239
Our whole family loved it.

34:49.900 --> 34:52.010
If we make them again, you should come and have some with us.

34:52.030 --> 34:53.550
We can have a family banquet together.

34:53.590 --> 34:54.110
Sure.

34:54.110 --> 34:55.780
I happen to also live in this neighborhood.

34:55.810 --> 34:56.760
When it's convenient for you,

34:56.760 --> 34:58.470
just let Xifan send me a message on WeChat.

34:58.630 --> 34:59.700
What a coincidence!

35:00.030 --> 35:01.280
We live so close.

35:01.610 --> 35:02.380
Great.

35:02.400 --> 35:04.680
Feel free to come over for a meal whenever you have time.

35:04.720 --> 35:06.630
Well, I won't disturb you any longer today.

35:06.630 --> 35:07.360
I'm leaving now.

35:07.360 --> 35:08.150
Alright, alright.

35:08.150 --> 35:10.240
Feel free to come over for a meal whenever you have time.

35:10.240 --> 35:11.240
Come over to hang out when you have time.

35:11.240 --> 35:11.960
Sure, sure.

35:11.960 --> 35:12.720
Bye-bye.

35:12.720 --> 35:13.760
Goodbye.

35:13.760 --> 35:14.840
Good night.

35:16.360 --> 35:18.760
My goodness, he's so handsome.

35:19.580 --> 35:21.630
I don't need to arrange blind dates for her anymore.

35:21.650 --> 35:22.560
That young man

35:22.630 --> 35:24.030
is tall, fair-skinned,

35:24.030 --> 35:25.030
and well-mannered.

35:25.030 --> 35:26.280
And he's very polite.

35:26.280 --> 35:28.990
Yes. He took such good care of our daughter.

35:29.960 --> 35:30.510
Look at you.

35:30.540 --> 35:32.180
Are you throwing up? How much did you drink?

35:32.330 --> 35:39.770
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

35:35.540 --> 35:36.400
I'll get you some water.

35:40.450 --> 35:48.130
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

35:41.840 --> 35:43.430
Just take this to pay the fee.

35:43.670 --> 35:44.240
Okay, okay.

35:44.240 --> 35:45.030
Thank you, doctor.

35:45.030 --> 35:45.510
It's fine.

35:45.510 --> 35:46.720
I'll come back next week.

35:46.720 --> 35:47.760
Alright.

35:48.700 --> 35:55.960
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

35:56.260 --> 36:03.210
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

35:57.670 --> 35:58.360
Are you awake?

36:02.420 --> 36:03.710
Your alcohol tolerance is terrible.

36:04.070 --> 36:06.650
♫A gentle breeze begins to rise♫

36:04.720 --> 36:06.040
It's this late, and you still haven't woken up.

36:07.930 --> 36:12.480
♫You'll see a rainbow♫

36:12.500 --> 36:14.710
♫Hovering in mid-air♫

36:15.820 --> 36:18.430
♫This sweet dream♫

36:20.430 --> 36:25.430
♫All our days are filled with♫

36:25.460 --> 36:29.040
♫Lololove and sunshine♫

36:29.480 --> 36:37.370
♫Close your eyes, and love will never fade away♫

36:37.490 --> 36:44.920
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

36:38.190 --> 36:40.620
I've prescribed you some medicine. See you later.

36:45.600 --> 36:53.290
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

36:53.850 --> 37:01.110
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

37:01.270 --> 37:08.210
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

37:25.590 --> 37:30.460
♫All our days are filled with♫

37:30.490 --> 37:34.040
♫Lololove and sunshine♫

37:39.880 --> 37:40.990
Still not awake?

37:40.990 --> 37:42.290
I'm already downstairs.

37:42.370 --> 37:43.410
Hurry up and come down.

37:43.430 --> 37:44.550
I've got your medicine ready.

38:08.510 --> 38:09.190
You're down?

38:15.840 --> 38:16.720
What's wrong with you?

38:16.920 --> 38:18.070
Still not fully awake?

38:21.110 --> 38:22.870
You had to drink so much last night.

38:23.030 --> 38:24.110
You downed each shot in two gulps.

38:24.990 --> 38:26.670
I thought you were a tough girl.

38:31.440 --> 38:32.110
What's wrong?

38:32.110 --> 38:32.920
Are you feeling unwell?

38:34.110 --> 38:35.880
The person you said

38:36.400 --> 38:38.550
you met in April last night—

38:39.440 --> 38:40.470
was it me?

38:41.400 --> 38:42.740
Of course.

38:44.720 --> 38:45.840
This is what you've been doubting?

38:46.920 --> 38:49.110
Haven't I made it obvious enough?

38:54.920 --> 38:56.030
Before,

38:56.320 --> 38:58.440
I felt the timing wasn't right,

38:58.770 --> 39:00.250
so I didn't say it directly.

39:01.280 --> 39:03.240
Last night, there were too many people,

39:03.240 --> 39:04.440
and I didn't want you to feel awkward,

39:04.590 --> 39:06.150
so I didn't make it very clear either.

